          "answerGuidance": [
            "Voltage drop",
            "Reduction in electrical potential",
            "Loss of electrical pressure",
            "Potential difference across a resistance"
          ]
        },
        {
          "questionText": "When does voltage drop occur in a standard electrical circuit?",
          "answerGuidance": [
